title: New: R. A. Rosenborg – Empire State
body:
San Diego’s **R.**

**A. Rosenborg** feels like he’s drifted straight from the Garden State soundtrack, and I mean that in entirely the best manner possible. New track, Empire State, is a perfectly penned indie number, with hints of Vampire Weekend, Death Cab For Cutie and pre-Fun. band The Formant. Stream it below and grab a download from [Bandcamp](http://rarosenborg.bandcamp.com/track/empire-state).

_when I am the Empire State, I hope you’ll be my Golden Gate_
